 ('GASTRONOMY','<001>GASTRONOMY<002>It is the study of the relationship between food and culture, art of preparing and serving rich or delicate and appetizing food, a style of cooking from particular region and the science of good eating.<003><004><005>COOKERY; COOKING; CUISINE; CULINARY SCIENCE<006>CULINARY ART<007><008>Culinary Arts<009><0010>','2017-11-07 10:48:22','2018-02-01 15:23:14','abram','abram',130,''),
