 ('CANNING (MEAT PRESERVATION)','<001>CANNING (MEAT PRESERVATION)<002>Done by adding a chemical preserving agent, by seal proofing and by pasteurizing the can (Reyes and Roldan, 2006).<003>MEAT PRESERVATION METHODS<004><005>COOKING; DRYING; FREEZING; SALTING; SMOKING<006><007><008>Culinary Arts<009><0010>Reyes, Dick. (2006).  Introduction to Culinary Operations.  Paranaque City: AR Skills Development and Mangement Services, 2006.','2017-11-28 10:23:14','2017-11-28 11:25:39','abram','abram',412,NULL);
