 ('WHITE STOCK','<001>WHITE STOCK<002>It has white meat and aromatic vegetables which are partly and lighly roasted in fat.  The color is developed by controlled reduction (Reyes and Roldan, 2006).<003>STOCKS (COOKING)<004><005>BROWN STOCK; FISH STOCK; VEGETABLE STOCK<006><007><008>Culinary Arts<009><0010>Reyes, Dick. (2006).  Introduction to Culinary Operations.  Paranaque City: AR Skills Development and Mangement Services, 2006.','2017-11-28 10:53:48','2017-11-28 10:53:48','abram','abram',421,NULL);
