 ('EARLY MODERN TOURISM','<001>EARLY MODERN TOURISM<002>The transitional era between premodern tourism (about AD 1500) and modern mass tourism (since 1950) (Weaver, David and Lawton, Laura. (2014).<003><004>GRAND TOUR; SEASIDE RESORTS; SPA RESORTS<005>CONTEMPORARY TOURISM; PREMODERN TOURISM<006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>Weaver, David and Lawton, Laura. (2014).  Tourism management.  Australia: Wiley.','2017-12-05 11:58:26','2017-12-05 13:16:18','abram','abram',532,'');
