 ('URBAN AREAS','<001>URBAN AREAS<002>Urban areas are usually home to man-made attractions such as theme parks, museums, or vintage sculptures and architecture. They also attract tourists for gourmet food and local culinary experiences (Tourism management, 2016).<003>GEOGRAPHICAL MILIEUS<004><005>COASTS AND BEACHES; DESERT REGIONS; ISLANDS; MOUNTAINOUS REGIONS; RURAL AREAS<006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>Tourism Management. (2016).  Tutorials Point (I) Pvt. Ltd.','2017-12-13 11:52:32','2017-12-13 11:55:21','abram','abram',670,''),
