 ('DESTINATION MARKETING','<001>DESTINATION MARKETING<002>Advertising and promotions, aimed at consumer and trade, designed to build awareness and desire to travel to a particular location. <003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>https://www.destinationnsw.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Tourism-Business-Toolkit-VOL1-Chapter7.pdf','2018-01-11 14:48:35','2018-02-20 16:29:26','abram','abram',869,'');
