 ('FAMILIARIZATION TOURS','<001>FAMILIARIZATION TOURS<002>Organized trips for travel agents, tour operators, tour wholesalers or other members of the travel trade for the purpose of educating and â€œfamiliarizingâ€ them with tourism destinations. By seeing the destinations where they are sending travelers, the travel trade is better prepared to answer customer questions and promote travel to the location.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 14:51:17','2018-01-11 14:51:17','abram','abram',873,'');
