 ('FREE INDEPENDENT TRAVEL','<001>FREE INDEPENDENT TRAVEL<002>Individual travel in which a tour operator has previously arranged blocks of rooms at various destinations in advance for use by individual travelers. These travelers travel independently, not in a group, usually by rental car or public transportation.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 14:52:14','2018-01-11 14:52:14','abram','abram',874,''),
 ('GROUPS INDEPENDENT TRAVEL','<001>GROUPS INDEPENDENT TRAVEL<002>Group travel in which individuals purchase a group package in which they will travel with others along a pre-set itinerary.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 14:53:03','2018-01-11 14:53:03','abram','abram',875,''),
