 ('INCENTIVE HOUSE','<001>INCENTIVE HOUSE<002>A package tour operator, wholesaler or travel agency that primarily organises, packages and sells incentive travel. <003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>file:///D:/LTM%20eresources/Terms/Tourism-Business-Toolkit-VOL1-Chapter7.pdf','2018-01-19 10:36:35','2018-01-19 10:36:35','abram','abram',1065,'');
