 ('SITE INSPECTION','<001>SITE INSPECTION<002>An assessment tour of a destination or facility by a meeting planner, convention or trade show manager, site selection committee, tour operator, wholesaler or incentive travel manager to see if it meets their needs and requirements prior to selecting a specific site for an event. After site selection, a site inspection may be utilized to make arrangements.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 15:11:44','2018-01-11 15:11:44','abram','abram',886,''),
 ('SPOUSE PROGRAM','<001>SPOUSE PROGRAM<002>Special activities planned for those who accompany an attendee to a convention, trade show or meeting. Note that programs today are not simply for women, but rather for men and women, spouses and friends. Programs must be creatively designed to interest intelligent and curious audiences.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 15:12:38','2018-01-11 15:12:38','abram','abram',887,''),
 ('TARGET RATING POINTS','<001>TARGET RATING POINTS<002>Statistical measurement which allows one to evaluate the relative impact of differing advertising campaigns.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009><0010>','2018-01-11 15:13:48','2018-01-11 15:13:48','abram','abram',888,'');
