 ('BREAST QUARTER (CHICKEN PARTS)','<001>BREAST QUARTER (CHICKEN PARTS)<002>Generally includes a little more than one quarter of the meat on the chicken. The cut includes half a breast, a wing, and part of the back.<003>CHICKEN PARTS (COMPOSITION AND STRUCTURE)<004><005>WHOLE CHICKEN; POULTRY HALF; BREAST; BREAST HALVES; WINGS; DRUMMETES; WINGETTES; WING TIPS; LEG QUARTERS; LEGS; THIGHS; DRUMSTICKS; GIBLETS<006><007>Cooking<008>Culinary arts<009>English<0010>http://www.recipetips.com/kitchen-tips/t--365/chicken-description-of-parts.asp. Retrieved January 27, 2018.','2018-01-27 10:40:14','2018-01-27 12:05:32','tina','tina',1177,'');
