 ('TOURISM SYSTEM','<001>TOURISM SYSTEM<002>It composes of different elements that have both spatial and functional dimensions that interact with physical, natural, social, cultural, economic, and technological factors.<003><004>CULTURAL ATTRACTIONS; EPHEMERAL ATTRACTIONS; ICONIC ATTRACTIONS; NATURAL ATTRACTIONS; TOURIST ATTRACTIONS<005><006><007><008><009><0010>Catibog-Sinha, C.S. (2012).  Sustainable tourism: Concepts and case studies in the Philippines, Caring for nature, culture, and people.  Quezon City: Haribon Foundation, Inc.','2018-02-07 16:30:57','2018-02-07 16:30:57','abram','abram',1336,'');
