 ('PROFESSIONAL TRAVELER','<001>PROFESSIONAL TRAVELER<002>A person for whom travelling has become a way of life.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009>ENGLISH<0010>Walker, John R. and Walker, Josielyn T. (2011). Tourism: concepts and practices. Boston: Prentice Hall.','2018-02-15 11:41:49','2018-02-15 11:41:49','chezka','chezka',1444,''),
 ('RELIGIOUS TRAVEL','<001>RELIGIOUS TRAVEL<002>Travel to satisfy one`s religious convictions and/or fulfill one`s curiosity about a particular faith or practice.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009>ENGLISH<0010>Walker, John R. and Walker, Josielyn T. (2011). Tourism: concepts and practices. Boston: Prentice Hall.','2018-02-15 11:42:15','2018-02-15 11:42:15','chezka','chezka',1445,''),
