 ('SEASONALITY','<001>SEASONALITY<002>The peaks and valleys of demand for a destination and its facilities.<003><004><005><006><007><008>LTM<009>ENGLISH<0010>Walker, John R. and Walker, Josielyn T. (2011). Tourism: concepts and practices. Boston: Prentice Hall.','2018-02-15 11:45:19','2018-02-15 11:45:19','chezka','chezka',1451,''),
