 ('ADAPTATION','<001>ADAPTATION<002>The meaning of a work to fit another medium while retaining the action, character, and as much a possible, the language and tone of the original.<003><004><005>IMITATION; PLAGIARISM<006><007><008>Philippine Literature<009>English<0010>Thesaurus on Philippines Literature','2019-08-04 03:11:06','2019-08-04 03:11:06','abram','abram',1501,'');
