 ('AESTHETICS (ARTS)','<001>AESTHETICS (ARTS)<002>A study of the emotions and the mind in relation to their sense of beauty in literature as distinguished from moral, social, political, practical, or economic considerations.<003><004><005><006><007>Beauty; Taste<008>Philippine Literature<009>English<0010>Thesaurus on Philippines Literature','2019-08-04 03:13:45','2019-08-04 03:13:45','abram','abram',1502,''),
