 ('ALLEGORY','<001>ALLEGORY<002>A method of representation in which a person, abstract idea, or event stands for itself or something else.<003><004><005><006><007><008>Philippine Literature<009>English<0010>Thesaurus on Philippines Literature','2019-08-04 03:18:57','2019-08-04 03:18:57','abram','abram',1505,'');
